Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.12,0:01:19.35,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eeny,meeny,miny,moe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.63,0:01:22.29,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,much the same
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.29,0:01:24.55,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.83,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm enjoying the view from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.54,0:01:48.33,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Pike or shield?  負けたくはない でも傷つけたくもない
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.77,0:01:51.32,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手に取って 確かめてた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.85,0:01:53.52,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,きっと戻れないんだって
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.84,0:01:58.97,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Whose side are you on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.17,0:02:01.75,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  思い出は枷
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.75,0:02:04.27,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  後付けのlove
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.27,0:02:07.08,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don't want to know!  優しさは仇
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.26,0:02:11.44,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We have always stood on the borderland.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.87,0:02:14.13,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,広げる両手 keep balance
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.43,0:02:19.36,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,より高く飛べる方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.72,0:02:29.01,OP_jp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守りたいよ 僕らの翼のないこの背中に背負った
